Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,距今約1800年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:07.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,中國處於群雄三分天下 爭奪霸權的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,劉備率領的蜀國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:11.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,曹操率領的魏國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孫權率領的吳國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:14.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即歷史上的三國時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在三雄互相制衡的三國時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誕生出了數不清的豪傑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他們的英勇事跡 至今仍為人們傳頌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:25.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,公元234年 五丈原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:28.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀軍陣中暗潮湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀帝劉備已然駕崩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀軍在與魏國司馬懿率領的大軍對峙時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:39.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀國丞相諸葛孔明已病入膏肓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,丞相 丞相 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這場仗要輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,失去了眾多戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打敗了一個又一個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:00.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的命數也到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:03.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:03.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,丞相？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-丞相！ -下一次人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:08.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能在無需拼個你死我活的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:10.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能在無需拼個你死我活的\N（二三四年 諸葛孔明逝世）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（二三四年 諸葛孔明逝世）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和平世界\N（二三四年 諸葛孔明逝世）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:13.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,轉世重生\N（二三四年 諸葛孔明逝世）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,轉世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:22.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（派對咖孔明）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:52.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我應該已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡就是地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（孔明 降臨於澀谷）\N萬聖節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:21.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你這打扮是孔明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我姓諸葛 名亮 字孔明…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好狠 超入戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明？誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是那人啊 超高智商一億的軍師？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,智商一億
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-他們是地獄的獄卒嗎 -還原度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好樣的 喝吧 用力喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喉嚨像火燒一樣刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,地獄刑法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明酒量不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是最頂級的龍舌蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:52.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這也是地獄的折磨 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我太欣賞你了 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去俱樂部吧 俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是下一個地獄嗎 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我甘願接受這極刑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來 死後的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟是如此吵鬧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（關於選拔）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又沒過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我帶孔明來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:25.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超像孔明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直抵內心深處的噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便是已死之人 也難以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這聲音的源頭是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Be crazy for me　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Make me shine on you　　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You're gonna see me 　　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,When you hear my music　　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'll be there for you　　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,No matter where you go　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,How do you see me from your point of view　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I steal your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,地獄的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何等華美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:09.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌聲如揚子江的濁流一般湧入體內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,根本沒人聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是不是沒才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒這回事 你很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:25.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才能又不是努力就能獲得的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才那美妙的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我佩服得五體投地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何以在地獄裡遇見歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,地獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請帶我見識更深的地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想率領亡者的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與英靈們打上一仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該來幫幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 注意別喝多了 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何嘗不是一個好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,發現孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你上哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還沒喝夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,地獄的折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-喝喝喝 -那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽你歌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:21.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再見 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 天亮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該死的司馬懿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這歌聲太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:13.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Everything seemed to be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:19.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Cause you gave me whispers of love all night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽這聲音 你是地獄的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是你把我帶到這裡來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說誰是地獄的歌姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可是你的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是放你睡在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你現在已經被凍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何以在地獄凍死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有完沒完 這裡才不是地獄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是地獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那這裡到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:57.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我年輕時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼幻術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不就是普通的鏡子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鏡子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這如水一般清澈的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道說…不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我應該在五丈原死了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就連《奇門遁甲》中都沒有記載轉生之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我復活了也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這心跳不是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,酒醒了就趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說你該不會動歪腦筋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我想了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以我的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:39.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這個世道為了人民一統天下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也未嘗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:41.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,忘記自我介紹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我姓諸葛 名亮 字孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:53.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我叫月見英子 叫我英子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌姬的芳名叫英子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你好像既沒錢包 也沒智慧型手機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,智慧型手機是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？難道你用翻蓋機？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種書籍叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,文字飄來飄去 時有時無
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如此小的物體中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟有如此精緻的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是老頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝點水冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:20.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,猶如蟬殼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:22.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是塑膠瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:26.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 那長針和短針轉動的東西有何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,時鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 水燒開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趕緊把火滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加濕器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-英子 -空調
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-英子 -電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那東西我也不知道是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:44.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世上還有很多我不知道的事物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我反而想問你知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至少傳授一下這智慧型手機的使用方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不要呢 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我看來 才能不是與生俱來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而是通過學習掌握的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,待我獲得智慧的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,定將報答您的恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以教到打工前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問這區塊鏈究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整整問了我四個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都說了 我是諸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,維基百科上也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真搞不懂了 這設定還要用多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再說了 這個叫孔明的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是古代的中國人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但你日語不是很流利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都沒注意到 自然而然就說起日語了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,文字也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彷彿生前就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以自然地理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彷彿一切都早已安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,根據維基的描述
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你不是早就死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我猜測是因為某種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被送到這個時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,設定太粗略了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,黃巾之亂 官渡之戰 赤壁之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後世是這樣流傳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好好 我還要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先去洗把臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,216年 曹操進魏王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,219年 劉備進漢中王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:15.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,263年 11月…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:19.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（263年11月 蜀漢滅亡）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:28.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀果然滅亡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:35.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後來司馬一族奪取了天下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而也沒能持續太久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,亂世再次到來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後又過了1800年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:46.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,熟悉的面孔 也早已不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:32.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Everything seemed to be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Cause you gave me whispers of love all night
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Uh-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:44.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But I'm alone tonight　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:50.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I just wanna get you out of my mind　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You don't know how much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是思念重要之人的情歌吧\NYou don't know how much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是思念重要之人的情歌吧\NBut you don't wanna be with me any more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But you don't wanna be with me any more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:01.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明\NI'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:03.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明\NI'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:04.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You are so far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起創造天下太平\NYou are so far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:07.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,You are so far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:07.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Even though you have broken my heart baby　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有戰爭的世界吧\NEven though you have broken my heart baby　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Even though you have broken my heart baby　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive today　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And miss you all day　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:25.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I just thought I could not live without you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:30.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Now I don't know what to do with myself　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:40.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm stronger than I think and I'm still in love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的歌聲有鼓舞人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而還是業餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,業餘是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相當於見習？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過 昨天在俱樂部聽見的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我看來純屬噪音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你當時不是特別嗨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 你太土了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你得掌握現在的流行趨勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼有奇怪的嘰喳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:11.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是笛子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,電子舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:15.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌唱得倒是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對這個時代的音樂非常感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 我在這世界還很無知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:30.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想不斷增長見聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明肯定也會愛上音樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了籌備軍費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望你能幫我介紹工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無業啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說自己是孔明的神經病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要說真名哦 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我姓諸葛 名亮 字孔明 -都說了 不是角色名！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老闆 冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然你說你是孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我想問問你為什麼要派馬謖守街亭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬謖是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬肉刺身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬謖是孔明很器重的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明力排眾議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將要地的防守任務交給了馬謖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而結果是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他沒能擋住敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,輸掉了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼 你偏袒了自己的徒弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然你是孔明 那你肯定能回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當時蜀國人才匱乏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我渴望得到新的軍官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:40.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當時確實有人推舉魏延 吳懿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但那樣一來 就永遠無法培養後繼軍官了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果只是為了阻止敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬謖可以輕鬆辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是這樣判斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而事與願違
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你太抬舉馬謖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬謖似乎預想過攻打長安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放敵人通過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:05.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許是為了催促我強攻長安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你意思是他不是沒守住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而是精心策劃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可能只是我的一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼了 在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:16.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,揮淚斬馬謖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明為了正軍紀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,含淚處死了失敗的馬謖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明也太嚴厲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,失去那人才太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這傢伙超有孔明範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服裝也好講究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過 我喜歡更樸素點的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老闆？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一直在找能跟我聊三國的員工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最近的年輕人都不讀三國了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,錄用了 錄用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以今天就開始上班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我終於也把孔明招入麾下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有 衣服就穿這身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 後面就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快到營業時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:06.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 你的眼罩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為昨天是萬聖節…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟夏侯惇一樣 多帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,三國宅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都是多虧了英子的助力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對 對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再榨點青檸汁就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然沒過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:36.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說 調酒的方法和價格 能記住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 勉強記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是有不明白的地方 就儘管問我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 我想請教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在放的這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:49.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比昨晚放的柔和很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:50.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:52.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛開始營業時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會放一段時間BPM100左右的慢歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,BPM是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,指的是歌曲的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,昨天放的歌大概是130到160左右
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,節奏快更興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我記得張飛在開懷痛飲時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,周圍人拍手的節奏也很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們是不是聊三國了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我的酒還沒好嗎 -來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:19.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趕緊來結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天超忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,點琴通寧和德貴麗的客人 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,點馬丁尼和百加地的客人 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鹹狗和琴通寧 含稅1700日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,刷卡支付 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你真是第一次做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比沏茶簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-啤酒 -我也要啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-來杯螺絲起子 -冰沙德貴麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雞尾酒交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我負責上啤酒和結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 換我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來杯迷霧之城…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Now what can you see with your eyes?）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:15.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（那視線望著的是 (True faith)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（究竟勾勒著怎樣的命運呢 (True fate)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的歌聲果然美妙\N（究竟勾勒著怎樣的命運呢 (True fate)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（究竟勾勒著怎樣的命運呢 (True fate)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太可惜了\N（究竟勾勒著怎樣的命運呢 (True fate)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（究竟勾勒著怎樣的命運呢 (True fate)）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:22.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Let me see it wow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子不該待在我們這種\N（Let me see it wow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂活動很弱的俱樂部\N（Let me see it wow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂活動很弱的俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:26.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（醒不來的夢看不到盡頭）\N音樂活動很弱的俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加入大型事務所成長空間更大啊\N（醒不來的夢看不到盡頭）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（醒不來的夢看不到盡頭）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:29.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大型事務所是？\N（醒不來的夢看不到盡頭）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大型事務所是？\N（Let me feel it wow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:31.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想…魏軍\N（Let me feel it wow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想…魏軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:33.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此\N（Dive into the new world）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:34.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Dive into the new world）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子好像特別信任你啊\N（Dive into the new world）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子好像特別信任你啊\N（Dreams come alive）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Dreams come alive）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,具體原因我就不深究了\N（Dreams come alive）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,具體原因我就不深究了\N（Reach for the top）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就她而言 還挺稀奇的\N（Reach for the top）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:42.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Reach for the top）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:42.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過\N（Dreams will come true）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Dreams will come true）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你可千萬別背叛她哦\N（Dreams will come true）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:47.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你可千萬別背叛她哦\N（We'll find the lights）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（We'll find the lights）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明剛來就直接工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有 能聽到英子美妙的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,疲憊都煙消雲散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:05.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虧你能一本正經地說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就不會害臊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我倒是挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連想說的話都沒能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就這樣在戰場上逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣的生命我看太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直接的意見 坦率的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須在活著的時候說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子為什麼選擇了音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我上高中時發生過很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當時心情極度低落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,修學旅行來澀谷時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:46.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚有特別嘉賓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要死等演完再說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當時的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那人的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我顫抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我後來才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那人原來是美國的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:11.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我當時就想 這哪還能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:14.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想像她一樣感動別人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:21.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我已經想放棄當歌手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡唱歌 也想堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但選拔總是落選
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:28.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,懷疑自己沒有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:33.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說實話 我覺得是時候放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為被你歌聲拯救的人 就在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:51.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你擁有表達自己感情的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我比任何人都確信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且 你如果放棄當歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想必會讓粉絲傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪來的粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不就在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,三次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的歌 我聽了三次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這震撼心靈的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想讓更多人感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,三顧之禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你有如此志向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我身為在茅廬讀書之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不回報豈不是不義之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要成為你的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的夢想是出道？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是吸引一萬名觀眾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論夢想是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論這條路有多麼艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:45.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我孔明定將傾盡全力輔佐你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你隨時可以向我下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:52.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我願貢獻綿薄之力 為你出謀劃策
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下令…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人設真堅定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你都說到這個份上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,受不了 這也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搞得我又想再努努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為這樣最好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:12.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（來段心情上好↑↑的）
